00:09:54,790 --> 00:09:55,650
Sorry.

142
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,370
Sir, this way, please.

143
00:10:09,270 --> 00:10:10,770
You can change your clothes this way.

144
00:10:10,790 --> 00:10:11,890
Mr. Lee, stairs.

145
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:16,650
Wait.

146
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,650
Mr. Lee needs to clean his clothes.

147
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:19,770
It's inconvenient for you to go in.

148
00:10:19,790 --> 00:10:21,010
Just wait at the door.

149
