Mr. Lee.

150
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:27,300
The threshold.

151
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,010
Use the iron to dry the clothes.

152
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,060
Make some noise.

153
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:48,890
Are you okay?

154
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:52,820
It's fine, go ahead.

155
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:54,420
Wang Jingwei's men

156
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,420
sent people to blow up the flour mill.

157
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,060
Cao Yuanzhong and some others
have been safely evacuated.

158
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,890
But all the brothers
on the perimeter died.

159
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:02,570
It was Liang Jingyuan who blew up
the Shanghai Bureau.

160
00:11:03,710 --> 00:11:05,500
We already met him
at the hospital just now.

161
00:11:05,950 --> 00:11:07,690
He once served in the Suzhou Bureau.

162
00:11:07,710 --> 00:11:09,570
But he's always been in contact
with the Shanghai Bureau.

163
00:11:09,590 --> 00:11:11,410
I had long sent a report
to the superiors.

164
00:11:11,430 --> 00:11:12,690
Between local bureaus,

165
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:13,930
strict confidentiality
must be maintained.

166
00:11:13,950 --> 00:11:14,930
They didn't listen.

167
00:11:14,950 --> 00:11:16,220
Just when our work was seeing progress,

168
00:11:16,430 --> 00:11:17,770
the Shanghai Bureau was wiped out.

169
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,500
Luo Han, calm down first.

170
00:11:20,590 --> 00:11:22,020
We should've long stopped

171
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,140
having any hope in the BIS.

172
00:11:23,790 --> 00:11:25,260
Why are you saying
such taboo words again?

173
00:11:25,430 --> 00:11:27,410
If you break away from the BIS,
your family will be finished.

174
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,340
Besides, revolutions always
have a mix of good and bad.

175
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,570
The BIS isn't as bad as you think.

176
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:33,890
Alright, enough of that.

177
00:11:34,550 --> 00:11:36,770
Tonight, you must leave Shanghai.

178
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:38,500
They're waiting for you
to report work in Chongqing.

179
00:11:39,190 --> 00:11:40,530
But you must bring back the information

180
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:42,860
about Liang Jingyuan establishing
the Cryptography Institute.

181
00:11:43,310 --> 00:11:44,140
Since we can't break away,

182
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:47,050
I will try to find Cao Yuanzhong
as soon as possible

183
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:49,810
to restore the Shanghai Bureau
and communications with Chongqing.

184
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:50,770
It's not good.

185
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:53,690
We are not sure how much influence

186
