in the bureau rashly.

188
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:00,930
How about this,

189
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:02,050
they're unfamiliar with me.

190
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:03,650
I can act as your liaison

191
00:12:04,070 --> 00:12:06,050
and help you continue with
the Sword Thrust Operation.

192
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:06,860
Luo Han.

193
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,860
The Sword Thrust Operation
is not your mission.

194
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:11,500
No matter what,
you shouldn't be left behind

195
00:12:11,950 --> 00:12:13,140
to carry out the plan in the hide.

196
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:14,650
Gu Yangshan,

197
00:12:15,830 --> 00:12:18,050
the person I respected most before

198
00:12:18,070 --> 00:12:19,290
was my senior brother.

199
00:12:19,830 --> 00:12:21,170
After coming to Shanghai,

200
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:23,170
you are the comrade I admire the most.

201
00:12:23,190 --> 00:12:24,460
If you're carrying out the plan,

202
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,500
I'm willing to stay.

203
00:12:26,190 --> 00:12:27,410
Besides, I said before,

204
00:12:27,430 --> 00:12:28,690
if you and this little punk

205
00:12:28,710 --> 00:12:31,410
could make Takeda willingly
replace Joseph Lee's code,

206
00:12:31,430 --> 00:12:33,170
I would be at your disposal.

207
00:12:33,830 --> 00:12:35,410
It's time for me to keep my word.

208
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:37,930
Can you cut it out?

209
00:12:38,710 --> 00:12:39,890
You're the little punk.

210
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:41,170
Your whole family are little punks.

211
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:43,100
I'll tell you one last time.

212
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:46,690
I'm an actor.

213
00:12:47,190 --> 00:12:49,930
In this operation, I'm the leading role.

214
00:12:50,310 --> 00:12:51,570
I am the sword.

215
00:12:52,430 --> 00:12:53,690
Ding Yi, don't be mad.

216
00:12:53,950 --> 00:12:56,690
It's true that
I looked down on you before.

217
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:57,930
But I have to admit

218
00:12:58,190 --> 00:12:59,290
that I underestimated you.

219
00:13:01,550 --> 00:13:02,890
I'm willing to admit defeat.

220
00:13:03,430 --> 00:13:04,170
From now on,

221
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:07,340
I'll work for you two tirelessly

222
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,290
without any complaint.

223
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:14,690
For the Party-State...

224
00:13:15,070 --> 00:13:15,380
No.

225
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,290
For resisting Japan.

226
00:13:17,590 --> 00:13:18,620
And for the common people.

227
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:19,570
Go on stage.

228
00:13:19,950 --> 00:13:20,340
Dress up in costume.

229
00:13:21,670 --> 00:13:22,380
From today on,

230
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,500
Luo Han will be our liaison.

231
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,260
Yuyin Pavilion has a mixed crowd.

232
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,220
It's the hardest to monitor.

233
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,530
We'll meet here from now on.

234
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,380
After we enter Sanyangli,

235
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:35,140
if Luo Han encounters an emergency,

236
00:13:35,710 --> 00:13:38,260
dress up as a newsboy
delivering papers to Sanyangli.

237
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,770
If we see the message, we'll know

238
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:41,890
you want to contact us.

239
00:13:42,430 --> 00:13:44,260
We will find a way to meet in time.

240
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:49,020
With lofty ambitions aiming
for the clouds,

241
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:56,140
the treasured sword at the waist
shining a rainbow's gleam.

242
00:13:57,640 --> 00:14:00,140
The state of Yan is in peril.

243
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:03,140
The state of Qin seeks our destruction.

244
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:05,930
The rivers and mountains
are about to fall.

245
00:14:05,950 --> 00:14:10,020
No warriors rise to sweep away the foe.

246
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:12,650
Thankfully there is Jing Ke

247
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:15,650
to try to turn the tide.

248
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:17,930
I admire the bravery

249
00:14:17,950 --> 00:14:21,020
to break into the tiger's lair.

250
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:28,860
Entrusted with the fate of the state,
guided by loyalty and courage!

251
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:47,930
Mr. Lee, we've arrived.

252
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:50,890
Have them wait outside for me.

253
00:14:51,190 --> 00:14:51,620
Alright.

254
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:17,020
Mr. Wu.

255
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:17,740
Mr. Lee.

256
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:21,020
There are guests upstairs.

257
00:15:22,950 --> 00:15:24,410
I never noticed before.

258
00:15:25,550 --> 00:15:27,260
Look, when placed side by side,

259
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:29,260
