260
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:29,890
Really?

261
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:31,890
It's yours.

262
00:15:31,910 --> 00:15:32,290
I can't accept that.

263
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,930
We're such good friends.

264
00:15:35,670 --> 00:15:36,650
